buy(uint256).details: Transfers ownership of a token from the seller to the buyer and emits a Buy event.

params.tokenId: The ID of the token to buy.

constructor.details: Constructor that mints a new token and assigns it to the contract owner.

params.name_: The name of the ERC721 token.
params.symbol_: The symbol of the ERC721 token.

getPrice(uint256).details: Returns the price assigned to a token.

params.tokenId: The ID of the token to check.

isSetForSale(uint256).details: Returns whether a token is set for sale.

params.tokenId: The ID of the token to check.

returns._0: Whether the token is set for sale.

setForSale(uint256,uint256).details: Sets the price for a token and emits a SetForSale event.

params.amount: The price to assign to the token.
params.tokenId: The ID of the token to set the price for.

supportsInterface(bytes4).details: Overrides the supportsInterface function to include the IERC721Tradable interface.

params.interfaceId: The ID of the interface to check for support.

returns._0: Whether the contract supports the interface.
